quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  56,39,"Dental jeyaa…ìe e [mofte] adinoo…ìe …ìen"
  56,40,"e see…óaa…ìe jeyaa…ìe e [mofte] sakkitii…ìe …ìen"
  56,41,E wontiroo…ìe nano …ìen. Ko hom…ìe woni …ìen yim…ìe nano
  56,42,"[∆Åen] no e nguleendi e fatay…óam"
  56,43,e …óowdi curki …ìawluki
  56,44,"wonaa …ìuu…ìundi, wanaa teddundi"
  56,45,"Ado …óum, hari ko …ìe neeminaa…ìe"
  56,46,…ìe laatino hi…ìe deppitoo e bakkaat maw…ói …óin
  56,47,"hi…ìe wi'aynoo: \"Enee, si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ∆¥i'e, hara ko men immintinoytee…ìe"
  56,48,hay baabiraa…ìe amen adinoo…ìe …ìen
  56,49,"Maaku : \"Pellet, aram…ìe e sakkitii…ìe"
  56,50,ko moo…ìoytee…ìe e √±alaande anndaande waqutu mun
  56,51,"refti pellet, onon …ìee majju…ìe fennu…ìe [ummital]"
  56,52,"ko on nyaamoyay…ìe e leggal \"Zaqquumi\" ngal"
  56,53,ngal hebbiniroyton deedi
  56,54,yariron ngal kadi fatay…óam
  56,55,yariron wa yarugol ngelooba …óom…óaamba
  56,56,Ko …óum woni ko …ìe kottiigu !u! en √±alnde njo…ìdi diina
  56,57,"Ko Menen woni ko tagi on. Ha…ói goonginon [Men immintinay on]"
  56,58,On yi'ii on maniiyu mo rufoton
  56,59,"Ko onon tagata mo? Kaa ko Menen woni tagoo…ìe […óum]"
  56,60,Ko Menen hoddiri maayde nden hakkunde mon. Men wonaali adatee…ìe
  56,61,"e wattitugol yeruu…ìe mon, Men fu…ó…óira on e ko on anndah"
  56,62,Gom…óii hi…óon anndi tageede aranun …óum. Ko ha…ói waajito…óon
  56,63,On yi'ii kon ko remoton
  56,64,Ko onon fu…óinta …óum? Kaa ko Menen woni fu…óinoo…ìe …ìen
  56,65,"Si Men haajuno, pellet, Men wa…óayno ndu foron. Wattinon hi…óon haawoo [wi'a]"
  56,66,Menen ko men leptetee…ìe perte ko min nafqi ko
  56,67,wurin ko men ha…óaa…ìe
  56,68,On yi'ii ndiyam …óam yaroton …óam
  56,69,"E ko onon jippiniri …óam ka duule? Kaa ko Menen jippini […óam]"
  56,70,"Si Men haajuno, Men wa…óayno …óam kaa…ó…óam. Ko ha…ói yetton [Allah]"
  56,71,On yi'ii yiite nge hu…ì…ìoton ngen
  56,72,"E ko onon woodini wa…ói le…ó…óe mum? Kaa ko Menen woodini […óe]"
  56,73,"Men wa…óir ngen [yiite] waaju, e nafitor nge setotoo…ìe"
  56,74,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, Maw…óo On"